CHRISTMAS TREES
Polygroup®'s seasonal products have been brightening homes around the world   for over 25 festive years! Our goal is to produce the most realistic and highest   quality artificial Christmas trees, wreaths, and garlands possible. With natural   trees as a guide, we produce thousands of different tree types in a variety of   colors and sizes, ranging from elegant PVC tips to the more luxurious PE   branches. We offer simple unlit trees as well as prelit trees with premium   lighting that comes in clear, multicolored or our signature patented Surebright™ technology   which ensures that the lights will stay lit even if a bulb burns out, breaks or   loosens. In addition, our energy saving LED trees come with a Warmbright™  feature that   is designed to produce the same warm pleasing glow of incandescent bulbs. All of   our trees have been designed for easy setup and features hooked or hinged   branches sitting atop a sturdy stand. Each artificial Christmas tree comes with   either a 2-year or 5-year warranty. 
With our portfolio featuring thousands of tree types and seasonal products,   our team constantly creates new items that are at the forefront of each year's   trends. Of course, our customers' needs are our first priority; therefore,   whether you prefer a classic Fraser Fir, a designer Pink Colored Pine or our   exclusive Miracle Tree™, we can   easily customize a tree type, size, color or shape as requested. At Polygroup®,   we strive to offer the highest quality products for all of your holiday needs.   Please take time to browse a selected sample of our trees in the menu on the   left.




POOLS
Splish, Splash Through Summer 
Summer is the perfect time of the year for outdoor fun and activities. With   bright colors, fun themes, and sturdy construction, Polygroup® has developed tons   of exciting toys and above-ground swimming pools for you and your kids to enjoy   during the hot summer months. We offer a wide range of the best frame pools and   ring pools that can be easily set up right in your own backyard. Take a splash   in our pools and enjoy all the benefits without the hassle and expense of   installing and maintaining a permanent swimming pool. Every pool can come with   accessories such as ground and pool covers, maintenance kits, filters, and our   all-in-one patent pending SkimmerPlus™  filter pump,   which conveniently attaches to the side of your pool and keeps your water clean   through its built-in filtering system and continuous skimming function to remove   debris from the surface. 
To make your summer experience complete, we have a large selection of fun   inflatable toys for the pool and the backyard. From play centers and water   slides to inflatable floats and swim rings, we offer toys appropriate for all   ages - infants to adults. So whether you want to splash around in a Quick Set®   ring pool or just relax on one of our lounges, your entire family will have a   blast playing outdoors with our products. Please take time to browse a selected   sample of our pools and inflatable toys in the menu on the left. 


LIGHTING
Brightening Your Home
Polygroup®'s wide assortment of lighting options can provide the perfect   solution for every holiday season. From traditional and premium miniature lights   to C-type bulbs and outdoor decor, Polygroup®'s lighting designs combine   reliability with quality. In support of our sustainability efforts we also offer   LED lights, which are quickly becoming the light source of choice due to their   energy saving properties and durability. In fact, our signature Warmbright™  LEDs goes one   step further to combine all the benefits of LED lights with the same warm   pleasing glow of incandescent bulbs.
As a major supplier of seasonal lighting, Polygroup® aims to stay at the   forefront with innovation and awareness. Every lighting product we produce is UL   listed and certain light sets carry the Energy Star® logo, which ensures that   the product is energy efficient and cost effective. In addition, we recently   developed an environmentally friendly light string that complies with all U.S. and   international safety guidelines and regulations. 
Whatever your wishes this holiday season, Polygroup® has the right lighting   solution for you. To brighten a walkway, create ambiance in a room, or add a   little color to a tree, there is a Polygroup® lighting product guaranteed to make   your home warm and inviting. Please take time to browse a selected sample of our   lights in the menu on the left.


ORNAMENTS


AIRBEDS
Ultimate Comfort, Everyday Versatility
Nordic Peak™ provides the ultimate in comfort and support, just like a real   mattress. Built with versatility and quality in mind, airbeds from Polygroup® are   a perfect fit for every situation. Made of durable, heavy-duty,   puncture-resistant vinyl, Nordic Peak™ can be used indoors or outdoors. 
Nordic Peak™ feature a patented built-in air pump and a quick release air   valve that simplifies the task of setting up – making it a practical choice for   teens, adults and senior citizens. With the push of a button, your portable   airbed will begin to inflate until the individual air chambers are completely   filled resulting in maximum support and comfort.
            Ready in minutes and taken   down in seconds, our lightweight and compact airbeds can be easily stowed in the   storage bags provided. Sturdy, practical, and functional, Nordic Peak™ are the   perfect solution for home, travel or leisure.



TRADITIONAL UNLIT TREES











 








			  
			  	• Realistic and high quality PVC plastic tips available in many natural colors and 
				 tip combinations
				• Quick and easy to assemble
				• Available with hooked or pre-attached hinged branches
				• Sturdy plastic or folding metal tree stand included
				• Easy to store with optional off season storage bag
				• Flame retardant
 
Please visit your local retailer or Contact Us to view entire collection of Polygroup® Christmas trees and other holiday products.
					Polygroup® tree and light components are covered under one or more U.S. and 
					international patents.



TRADITIONAL PRELIT TREES










 








			  • Realistic and high quality PVC plastic tips available in many natural colors and tip  combinations
					• Pre-strung with clear or multi-color lights with lamp lock and anti-twist bulbs
					• Available with Surebright™ premium lights that stay lit even if a bulb burns out, breaks or loosens
					• Quick and easy to assemble
					• Available with hooked or pre-attached hinged branches
					• Sturdy plastic or folding metal tree stand included
					• Easy to store with optional off season storage bag
					• Available with remote control and on/off pedal switch
					• Extra bulbs and fuses included
					• Flame retardant
 
Please visit your local retailer or Contact Us to view entire collection of Polygroup® Christmas trees and other holiday products.
					Polygroup® tree and light components are covered under one or more U.S. and 
					international patents.



PERFECT SHAPE™ TREE










 








			  	• Realistic and high quality PVC and PE molded tips available in many natural colors and tip combinations
				• Perfect Shape™ Technology allows the branches to spring into shape
				• When one light burns out, breaks or loosens, the rest remain lit
				• Switch the lights on and off freely by remote controller or foot switch
				• Large selection of shapes and sizes from 4 feet to 30 feet
				• Pre-strung SureBright™ lights
				• Sturdy plastic or metal tree stand included
				• Easy to store with optional off season storage bag
				• Flame retardant
 
Please visit your local retailer or Contact Us to view entire collection of Polygroup® Christmas trees and other holiday products.
					Polygroup® tree and light components are covered under one or more U.S. and 
					international patents.



INSTANT PULL-UP™ TREE










 








				• Special design and construction with realistic green PVC tips make the tree look fresh and natural
				• Easy and quick one-minute set up
				• Sturdy plastic or metal tree stand included
				• If one bulb burns out, the rest stay lit
				• Easy to store with optional off season storage bag
				• Flame retardant
				
 
Please visit your local retailer or Contact Us to view entire collection of Polygroup® Christmas trees and other holiday products.
					Polygroup® tree and light components are covered under one or more U.S. and 
					international patents.



QUICK SET® TREE










 








				• Quick Set® technology design tree
				• Pole to pole electrical connection, tree is automatically lit once pole is connected
				• No extra plugs and cords to locate, only one from the tree base
