About Us






 




					Poly Group LLC is a technology company working to commercialize a highly-effective and biocompatible antimicrobial co-polymer. Poly Group has the exclusive worldwide license for this technology which was discovered in the labs at Purdue University. It is being marketed under the brand name Nouvex™.
Founded in 2011 and headquartered at the Purdue Research Park of Southeast Indiana in New Albany, Poly Group’s scientists custom create Nouvex™. formulas that can be easily integrated during the manufacturing process. Nouvex™. can be integrated into virtually any substrate, including paper, plastics, paints, glass, powder coatings and textiles.
				
 

